ote><br />\n<br />\n已經bk埋wifi蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"743eba8da68241055480e32b98fb5bd72ed6159f","tid":38191,"uid":63775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T18:50:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鼓浪嶼 廈門大學 中山路步行街 xx植物園 土樓<br />\n啲酒店自助餐幾抵<br />\n有時間可以去五通坐船去金門行下 半個鐘船</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nthx ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cf1fec9aed80c73fc90c1974edceed6e08abaed","tid":38191,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T19:06:13.000Z","msg":"去金門有咩行？無車牌"},{"pid":"620245b2126126bbffc8ac1fd71a78350056896c","tid":38191,"uid":18739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T19:09:32.000Z","msg":"日月谷溫泉度假村😗"},{"pid":"9517185d89dcb28e6ed326a6d48f69187235aec6","tid":38191,"uid":44025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:15:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鼓浪嶼 廈門大學 中山路步行街 xx植物園 土樓<br />\n啲酒店自助餐幾抵<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有時間可以去五通坐船去金門行下</span> 半個鐘船</blockquote><br />\n記住要護照同台證<br />\n利申月尾去金門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打係本島飛定廈門過 定係金門大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n廈門過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b009159287054f34e3765f991af0e6269ad36de","tid":38191,"uid":3080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:27:00.000Z","msg":"聖誕去廈門5日4夜,留個名先<br />\n淨係買咗高鐵飛,未買酒店<br />\n暫時諗住會去埋金門同永定土樓"},{"pid":"ba2776421a6d73ddeff8f6c426ee40358ee7ccbb","tid":38191,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:27:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聖誕去廈門5日4夜,留個名先<br />\n淨係買咗高鐵飛,未買酒店<br />\n暫時諗住會去埋金門同永定土樓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n金門有咩地方好行？"},{"pid":"4b28b451c46972df2a5ca9de74ed52f72e446b8c","tid":38191,"uid":64880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:08:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聖誕去廈門5日4夜,留個名先<br />\n淨係買咗高鐵飛,未買酒店<br />\n暫時諗住會去埋金門同永定土樓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n金門有咩地方好行？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇下國共當年打到幾行 蔣介石有幾緊張 到宜家仲有果種緊張氣氛 周圍可見還我河山<br />\n 條條村有軍營 個個沙灘有地雷 由廈門過去會好大反差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個feel唔係好多地方有 由其係人身安全情況下<br />\n<br />\n去金門搭車用台灣悠遊卡一卡通就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"344547b9aa4e46b522afc547ef518258a0aae2ba","tid":38191,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:11:15.000Z","msg":"消費物價，旅費如何<br />\n<br />\n係咪同去台灣差唔多，我指廈門加金門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b308ceac050ee303038dc4923e4b1164b453a36","tid":38191,"uid":17740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:15:05.000Z","msg":"廈門閩南大酒店 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62a1a78f2f32bc85619cffd2dfe41d1af4a0c6e","tid":38191,"uid":17740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:16:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廈門閩南大酒店 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n房都幾乾淨 雙人房都係400元晚"},{"pid":"5609d14305f5d8f79ff33f641c0f28d9fad2a2e7","tid":38191,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:30:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>消費物價，旅費如何<br />\n<br />\n係咪同去台灣差唔多，我指廈門加金門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n金門有數得計，去到金門買張1日交通卡，食飯錢，頂多買幾盒手信，500-1000港幣有多。佢有個商場賣名牌野，諗你都唔會有興趣。<br />\n<br />\n廈門就要睇你玩咩食咩。你日日去邪骨條數都唔細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eae7508a8972d1af1e2a99192a58dd3dc9a7c56","tid":38191,"uid":50739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:56:12.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"11f693f097c0ab0cd39589b2e673360158c22dff","tid":38191,"uid":50739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:58:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去金門有咩行？無車牌</blockquote><br />\n可以租電動車，around２百幾蚊一日，揸住架車兩日都夠玩"},{"pid":"4e1ed8630f2a819c684fc6a728becb3f208b87bc","tid":38191,"uid":44025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:31:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聖誕去廈門5日4夜,留個名先<br />\n淨係買咗高鐵飛,未買酒店<br />\n暫時諗住會去埋金門同永定土樓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n金門有咩地方好行？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇下國共當年打到幾行 蔣介石有幾緊張 到宜家仲有果種緊張氣氛 周圍可見還我河山<br />\n 條條村有軍營 個個沙灘有地雷 由廈門過去會好大反差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個feel唔係好多地方有 由其係人身安全情況下<br />\n<br />\n去金門搭車用台灣悠遊卡一卡通就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n基本上你唔鐘意歷史同軍事嘅話會覺得金門好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}